trick or treat ( also known as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and death at 33 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in foreign markets ) is a 1986 american supernatural horror film by de laurentiis entertainment group , starring marc price , and tony fields , with special appearances by gene simmons and ozzy osbourne . the film centers around a teenager who is haunted by the ghost of his rock hero . it is the directorial debut of actor charles martin smith .